Description:
"A new iphone version of the classic Freecell game! 
Freecell requires skill and strategy to win while offering hours of entertainment.
Freecell became popular as one of solitaire games included with Windows and now it's ready for you to enjoy on your mobile device with touch interface. Use the four free card spots to move all the cards to the Foundation stacks for a win.


You can play this app in your iPhone, iPod or iPad and for FREE!
With smooth drag and drop, clear and neat retina display graphics, you won't be looking for any other Freecell app.

Features includes: 
- Universal App;
- Easy drag and drop; 
- Auto fill card to foundation piles; 
- Portrait and landscape mode; 
- Easy to read and brand new original card set; 

- Gamecenter leaderboards: 
-- Games played 
-- Games won; 
-- Cumulative time played; 
-- Best times; 
-- Best moves; 
- Gamecenter Achievements with milestones as you progress into the game

Free version is iAd supported."

"'100 - Cups and Balls Edition HD' is simple but addicting app. Test your reaction in single tap game with realistic physics engine. 

Tap on screen to open the pot. Your purpose is to fill moving cups with falling balls. Filled cups will return balls to the pot. Empty cups will be unhooked from the moving chain. The game ends when all balls or cups are lost. Each level speeds up the cups. On higher levels cups will change color. Colored cups produces higher value colored balls. The longer you remain in the game, the more points you receive. 

• Physics engine; 
• Single tap control; 
• Short game (~5 min.); 
• Leaderboard; 
• Achievements; 
• Sounds and music."

"The story of Adelantado continues in Book Three – get ready for an epic conclusion of this amazing trilogy!
The sequel starts where the previous part left off. Don Diego finds himself on top of the high cliff. There he comes across a stone that tells the story of these ancient and mysterious lands and its beautiful but dangerous inhabitants. Despite the risks that lay ahead the brave explorer has to push forward and finish his quest to find the lost expedition.
On his way to a gigantic volcano visible afar our brave hero will be accompanied by his fellow crew members. Together they will build forts, discover ancient ruins and never-before-seen creatures of the forest, defend against the Neanderthals and help the locals.

Awesome new features, mesmerizing locations and quests, improved graphics and the last chapter of Don Diego's epic travel await you in Adelantado Trilogy: Book Three!

- New story about noble Adelantado;
- 10 challenging levels;
- Improved graphics;
- Mesmerizing locations and quests;
- Proven formula of its predecessors.

JOIN US! 

Enjoy Realore Games at: http://www.realore.com 
